column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.petror9#_r, p.dered_g, p.dered_r, p.dered_u, p.dered_g - p.dered_r as red, p.dered_, s.z as z_spec, s.zErr, zns.nvote, zns.p_el as elliptical, zns.p_cw as spiralclock, zns.p_acw as spiralanticlock, zns.p_edge as edgeon, zns.p_dk as dontknow, zns.p_mg as merger FROM galaxy as p JOIN ZooNoSpec AS zns ON p.objid = zns.objid JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE p.clean = # and zns.nvote > = # and zns.p_cw > # and red > .#
